        i0.ɵɵelementStart(283, "mat-card-content");
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(284, "p", 16);
        i0.ɵɵtext(285, " Colorado Festival of Horror 2022: Funhouse is thrilled to announce award-winning Special Guest Author Steve Rasnic Tem coming to our September 2022 convention on Saturday, September 10th! Steve will be meeting fans and signing books at the Hex Publishers table! Steve Rasnic Tem is a past winner of the Bram Stoker, World Fantasy, and British Fantasy Awards. His novel Ubo (Solaris Books), a finalist for the Bram Stoker Award, is a dark science fictional tale about violence and its origins, featuring such historical viewpoint characters as Jack the Ripper, Stalin, and Heinrich Himmler. He has published almost 500 short stories in his 40+ year career. Some of his best are collected in Thanatrauma and Figures Unseen from Valancourt Books. Steve also has the chilling short story \"Late Sleepers\" in Hex's It Came From the Multiplex: 80s Midnight Chillers anthology. The convention exclusive edition will be on sale at the show! Visit Steve's home on the web at ");
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(286, "a", 38);
