        i0.ɵɵelementStart(363, "mat-card-content");
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(364, "p", 16);
        i0.ɵɵtext(365, " Denver - \u201CColorado Festival of Horror (COFOH) 2022: Funhouse\u201D returns for our second year September 9, 10, and 11, 2022, at the Embassy Suites by Hilton Denver Central Park, 4444 N. Havana St, Denver, CO 80239. COFOH is an intimate fan experience and convention for all things horror, featuring celebrity guests, artists, writers, vendors, panels and so much more. In that screaming tradition COFOH is proud to announce actress, producer and director Lynn Lowry of THE CRAZIES and SHIVERS fame! ");
