        i0.ɵɵelement(367, "br");
        i0.ɵɵtext(368, " Lynn Lowry is an American born actress who\u2019s been performing, directing and producing for five decades. She is best known for the cult classic horror films, I DRINK YOUR BLOOD, THE CRAZIES, SHIVERS and CAT PEOPLE. But her professional career really began when at seventeen she acted opposite the sixteen-year-old John Belushi at the Shawnee Summer Theatre in Bloomfield, Indiana. Shortly after that Lynn went to New York where she starred opposite Peter Fonda in FIGHTING MAD directed by academy award winner, Jonathan Demme. She was a regular on the soap opera, HOW TO SURVIVE A MARRIAGE opposite F. Murray Abraham and Brad Davis and also acted in ANOTHER WORLD. ");
