        i0.ɵɵelement(370, "br");
        i0.ɵɵtext(371, " While in New York, Lynn studied all styles of theatre, becoming a producer and director at the Off-Broadway Theatre, The Production Company and did three plays at the famed Manhattan Theatre Club. In the past 20 years, Lynn has been singing with her jazz trio in Los Angeles and doing a multitude of Indy Films. She\u2019s won thirteen Best Actress Awards for her work in MODEL HUNGER, BASEMENT JACK, THE PERIPHERAL and READY FOR MY CLOSE-UP and three Lifetime Achievement Awards at various film festivals. ");
        i0.ɵɵelement(372, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelement(373, "br");
        i0.ɵɵtext(374, " Lynn Lowry was very fortunate to have had the opportunity to work with George A. Romero, David Cronenberg, David E. Durston, Paul Schrader and many more wonderful directors. They provided her with a priceless legacy that will never die. ");
